<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="close-v">close <strong><em>v</em></strong> ★</h1>
<p>英 /kləʊz/    美 /kloʊz/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1-shut">1.★ <strong>关闭（门窗等）；闭合；合上 (shut)</strong></h4>
<p>反 open </p>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>close the door / window / curtains
关门/关窗/拉上窗帘</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Beth <strong>closed</strong> her <strong>eyes</strong> and tried to sleep.
贝丝闭上眼睛想睡觉。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>close a book / an umbrella
合上书/收起伞</p></div>

<h4 id="2">2.★ <strong>（ 店 铺 等 暂 时 性 的 ） 关 闭 ； 歇 业 ； 结 束；倒闭：</strong></h4>
<p>反 open </p>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>What time does this bank close?
这家银行什么时候关门？</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>We close for lunch between twelve and two.
我们十二点到两点歇业用午餐。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Many factories have closed in the economic crisis.
很多工厂在经济危机中倒闭了。</p></div>

<h4 id="3">3.★ <strong>结束；停止：</strong></h4>
<p>反 open </p>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>The match closed at ten o’clock.
10点整比赛结束了。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>The manager <strong>closed</strong> the meeting <strong>with</strong> a short speech.
经理以简短的讲话结束了会议。</p></div>

<h4 id="4">4.<strong>接近；缩小：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>These measures are aimed at <strong>closing the gap</strong> between the rich and poor.
这些措施旨在缩小贫富差距。</p></div>

<h2 id="_2">固定搭配</h2>
<h3 id="close-down">close down</h3>
<p>1.<strong>关闭；停业：</strong>  </p>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>If I had stayed in this business just for the money, I would have closed down years ago.
从事这个行业如果只是为了钱，那么多年前我就不干了。</p><footer>2009 浙江</footer></div></div>